"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-09-Watch-Economic-benefits-of-hosting-the-Olympics-1vVsKnEW2Vq-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  The Paris Olympic Games, with a total cost surpassing 11 billion euros, will conclude on August 11. Amid France's economic instability, questions arise about whether the Olympics will stimulate the economy or burden Paris financially. Recent Games has consistently exceeded budget forecasts. What is the real return on investment for host cities? How has Beijing, the \\\"Dual Olympic City,\\\" influenced China's sports development after hosting both the Summer and Winter Games? This week's Biz Talk features Christophe Dubi, Olympic Games Executive Director, and Bi Weiduo, Sports Industry Partner at PwC, to decode the economic implications of \\\"Olympic fever.\\\"  CGTN  Copied  The Paris Olympic Games, with a total cost surpassing 11 billion euros, will conclude on August 11. Amid France's economic instability, questions arise about whether the Olympics will stimulate the economy or burden Paris financially. Recent Games has consistently exceeded budget forecasts. What is the real return on investment for host cities? How has Beijing, the \\\"Dual Olympic City,\\\" influenced China's sports development after hosting both the Summer and Winter Games? This week's Biz Talk features Christophe Dubi, Olympic Games Executive Director, and Bi Weiduo, Sports Industry Partner at PwC, to decode the economic implications of \\\"Olympic fever.\\\"  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\